    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦称与中国的债务重组谈判令人鼓舞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/pakistan-says-debt-reprofile-talks-with-china-are-encouraging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦财政部长表示，中国对巴基斯坦延长“一带一路”倡议相关债务期限的请求做出了令人鼓舞的回应，这意味着这个饱受过去高昂借贷压力的国家有了更多的喘息空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/pakistan-says-debt-reprofile-talks-with-china-are-encouraging</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 19:08:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长雷恩表示经济增长疲软可能加剧通货紧缩压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/ecb-s-rehn-says-weak-growth-could-increase-disinflation-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员奥利·雷恩表示，欧元区经济形势愈发严峻可能会加剧消费者价格增长放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/ecb-s-rehn-says-weak-growth-could-increase-disinflation-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gatemore 寻求回购瑞士手表并在美国上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/gatemore-pushes-watches-of-switzerland-for-buyback-us-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Gatemore Capital Management 已入股瑞士钟表集团有限公司 (Watches of Switzerland Group Plc)，并要求这家奢侈手表零售商积极回购股票，并考虑在美国上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/gatemore-pushes-watches-of-switzerland-for-buyback-us-listing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 17:28:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
